title: 05/07/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps the Adam Schefter interview that made headlines yesterday and discusses his takeaways from the discussion. Wisconsin area radio host Mike Heller joins us to talk what's next in the Aaron Rodgers saga. And Former NBA Player Rex Chapman calls in to talk about his new Podcast, "Charges with Rex Chapman"
